Reasoning: The paper deals with building new test sets for the CIFAR-10 and ImageNet datasets and evaluating the generalization ability of classification models. This falls under the domain of computer vision (cs.CV) and machine learning (cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.NE). Additionally, the paper involves natural language processing (NLP) techniques for data augmentation, which could also place it under the category of computational linguistics (cs.CL).
